"<html><head><meta name=\"qrichtext\" content=\"1\" /><style type=\"text/css\">\n"
"p, li { white-space: pre-wrap; }\n"
"</style></head><body style=\" font-family:\'MS Shell Dlg 2\'; font-size:7.8pt; font-weight:400; font-style:normal;\">\n"
"<p align=\"center\" style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:14pt; font-weight:600; font-style:italic;\">----VO PH CHA TRNH----</span><span style=\" font-family:\'MS Shell Dlg 2\',\'serif\'; font-size:14pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p align=\"center\" style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:14pt; font-weight:600; font-style:italic;\">-L Hu Trc-</span><span style=\" font-family:\'MS Shell Dlg 2\',\'serif\'; font-size:14pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt; font-weight:600;\">I. Tc gi</span><span style=\" font-family:\'MS Shell Dlg 2\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">- L Hu Trc (1724  1791) hiu l Hi Thng Ln ng, ngi lng Liu X, huyn ng Ho, ph Thng Hng, trn Hi Dng (nay thuc huyn Yn M, tnh Hng Yn).</span><span style=\" font-family:\'MS Shell Dlg 2\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">- ng l mt danh y, khng ch cha bnh m cn son sch v m trng dy ngh thuc  truyn b y hc.</span><span style=\" font-family:\'MS Shell Dlg 2\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">- Phn ln cuc i hot ng y hc v trc tc ca ng gn vi qu ngoi  x Sn Quang, huyn Hng Sn, tnh H Tnh.</span><span style=\" font-family:\'MS Shell Dlg 2\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">- B Hi Thng y tng tm lnh gm 66 quyn, l cng trnh nghin cu y hc xut sc nht ca ng trong thi trung i Vit Nam:</span><span style=\" font-family:\'MS Shell Dlg 2\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">+ Tc phm ghi li nhng cm xc chn tht ca tc gi trong nhng lc ln li i cha bnh  cc min qu, bc l tm huyt v c  ca ngi thy thuc.</span><span style=\" font-family:\'MS Shell Dlg 2\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">+ Qua tc phm, c th thy L Hu Trc cn l mt nh vn, nh th vi nhng ng gp ng ghi nhn cho vn hc nc nh.</span><span style=\" font-family:\'MS Shell Dlg 2\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt; font-weight:600;\">II. Tc phm</span><span style=\" font-family:\'MS Shell Dlg 2\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt; font-weight:600;\">1. Thng kinh k s</span><span style=\" font-family:\'MS Shell Dlg 2\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">- Thng kinh k s (K s n kinh ) l tp k s bng ch Hn, hon thnh nm 1783, c xp  cui b Hi Thng y tng tm lnh nh mt quyn ph lc.</span><span style=\" font-family:\'MS Shell Dlg 2\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">- K s: l mt th k, ghi chp s vic, cu chuyn c tht v tng i hon chnh.</span><span style=\" font-family:\'MS Shell Dlg 2\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">- Thng kinh k s t quang cnh  kinh , cuc sng xa hoa trong ph cha Trnh v quyn uy, th lc ca nh cha  nhng iu L Hu Trc mt thy tai nghe trong chuyn i t Hng Sn ra Thng Long cha bnh cho th t Trnh Cn v cha Trnh Sm. Qua , ngi c thy c thi  coi thng danh li ca tc gi. Tc phm kt thc vi vic L Hu Trc c v li qu nh, tr v vi cuc sng t do trong tm trng hn hoan, tip tc cng hin i mnh cho y thut.</span><span style=\" font-family:\'MS Shell Dlg 2\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt; font-weight:600;\">2. Vo ph cha Trnh</span><span style=\" font-family:\'MS Shell Dlg 2\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt; font-weight:600;\">2.1. Tm tt</span><span style=\" font-family:\'MS Shell Dlg 2\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\"> Vo sng sm tinh m ngy 1 thng 2, ti c lnh triu vo ph cha. Ti nhanh chng c iu i trn mt ci cng chy nh nga lng. Ti i vo t ca sau, nhn quanh ti thy cy ci um tm, chim ht lu lo, mun hoa ua thm. Qua my ln ca, cc hnh lang di quanh co ti c a ti mt ngi nh tht ln gi l phng tr.  c trong phng u c sn son thp vng. Lc  thnh thng ang ng phng thuc cng cc phi tn nn ti khng th yt kin. Ti c thit i ba sng m v vi  dng ton bng vng, bc. n xong ti c a n yt kin  ng Cung v khm bnh cho th t Trnh Cn. Th t v n qu no, mc qu m m sinh bnh. Na s b cun vo vng danh li, na v chu n ca nc. Cui cng, ti dc lng k n cho th t, ri t gi ln cng tr v kinh Trung Kin ch thnh ch. Bn b ai ai trong cung cng n thm hi.</span><span style=\" font-family:\'MS Shell Dlg 2\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt; font-weight:600;\">2.2. Tm hiu chung</span><span style=\" font-family:\'MS Shell Dlg 2\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">- B cc: 2 phn</span><span style=\" font-family:\'MS Shell Dlg 2\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">+ P1 (T u n xem mch ng cung cho tht k): Cuc sng ni ph cha c miu t con mt ca Hi Thng Ln ng</span><span style=\" font-family:\'MS Shell Dlg 2\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">+ P2 (cn li): Cnh L Hu Trc bt mch, k n cho th t Trnh Cn.</span><span style=\" font-family:\'MS Shell Dlg 2\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt; font-weight:600;\">2.2. Tm hiu chi tit</span><span style=\" font-family:\'MS Shell Dlg 2\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt; font-weight:600; font-style:italic;\">a. Quang cnh v cung cch sinh hot trong ph cha Trnh</span><span style=\" font-family:\'MS Shell Dlg 2\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt; font-weight:600; font-style:italic;\">a.1) Quang cnh</span><span style=\" font-family:\'MS Shell Dlg 2\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">- </span><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt; font-style:italic;\">ng vao phu</span><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">: My ln ca, mi ca u co v si canh gac, ai ra vao phai co the. Con ng i la nhng day hanh lang quanh co ni nhau lin tip. Vn hoa trong phu cy ci um tum, chim ku riu rit, danh hoa ua thm, gio a thoang thoang mui hng</span><span style=\" font-family:\'MS Shell Dlg 2\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">- </span><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt; font-style:italic;\">Trong phu</span><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">: Nha ai ng, Quyn bng, Gac tia vi  nghi trng sn son thp vang, sp thp vang, vong iu, mm vang chen bac,  n toan cua ngon vt la.</span><span style=\" font-family:\'MS Shell Dlg 2\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt; font-style:italic;\">- Ni cung</span><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">: 5 - 6 ln trng gm, trong phong thp nn, gia phong co mt cai sp thp vang, gh rng, nm gm, en sap, hng hoa ngao ngat.</span><span style=\" font-family:\'MS Shell Dlg 2\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">=&gt; n tng v ph cha l chn thm nghim, kn cng cao tng, v cng xa hoa trng l. Mu sc ch o l mu , vng, rc r ua nhau lp lnh. Cuc sng trong ph cha l cuc sng hng lc ca vua cha vi cung tn, m n, cnh p, mn ngon. Khng kh trong ph cha l mt khng kh ngt ngt t ng, ch thy hi ngi, phn sp, n nn, hng hoa ngo ngt m thiu hn s thanh thot ca kh tri.</span><span style=\" font-family:\'MS Shell Dlg 2\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt; font-weight:600; font-style:italic;\">a.2) Cung cch sinh hot</span><span style=\" font-family:\'MS Shell Dlg 2\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">- n ph cha phi c thnh ch, c th mi c vo.  dn ngi vo ph c mt tn y t chy ng trc ht ng, lnh em cng n ngi th chy nh nga lng khin ngi ngi trong cng d c n khm bnh m nh chu cc hnh b xc mt m kh khng ni ht.</span><span style=\" font-family:\'MS Shell Dlg 2\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">- Ph cha c c mt gung my phc v ng c, tp np. Nhng ngi gi ca quyn bo rn rng, ngi c vic quan qua li nh mc ci, v s canh gi ca cung, quan truyn ch chuyn vic truyn mnhCc danh y ca su cung, hai vin c tin c t mi ni ngi ch i, tc trc  phng tr, cc phi tn chu chc xung quanh thnh thng, ngi hu ng xung quanh th t, trong mn l che ngang sn l cc cung nhn ng xm xt.</span><span style=\" font-family:\'MS Shell Dlg 2\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">- Ph cha l ni quyn uy ti thng, bi vy tt c nhng li xng h, bm tu u phi rt knh cn, l php. Trong ph cn c l k hy rt c bit, king nhc n t thuc,.</span><span style=\" font-family:\'MS Shell Dlg 2\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">- Khm bnh cho th t phi tun theo mt lot cc php tc. Bt u l Ti nn th ng ch  xa. Ri thy thuc phi qu bn ly theo lnh ca quan chnh ng. Li theo lnh quan, thy thuc gi yu c php ngi bt mch,</span><span style=\" font-family:\'MS Shell Dlg 2\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">=&gt; Ph cha qu thc khng ch p lng ly, thm nghim m cn l chn uy quyn ti thng vi cung cach sng l nghi, khun phep tao nn khng khi trang nghim, kinh cn n ngt ngat. Tt c nhng g thng ch thy xut hin trong cung vua th nay xut hin trong ph cha. Cha c gi l Thnh thng, lnh cha c gi l Thnh ch,=&gt; uy quyn ln lt vua ca cha Trnh Sm.</span><span style=\" font-family:\'MS Shell Dlg 2\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">- C nhng chi tit trong tc phm tng thong qua nh ghi chp khch quan n thun song li bc l mt nhn quan k s su sc ca tc gi:</span><span style=\" font-family:\'MS Shell Dlg 2\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">+ </span><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt; font-style:italic;\">Chi tit v ni cung th t:</span><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\"> ng i ti om, my ln trng gm, quang cnh xung quanh phng: phng rng, gia l sp thp vng,=&gt; Nhng chi tit   ni ln ngun gc, cn nguyn ca cn bnh, ng thi t n cng phi by trc mt ngi c s hng lc, n chi ca ph cha.</span><span style=\" font-family:\'MS Shell Dlg 2\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">- Chi tit thy thuc gi yu trc khi khm bnh c truyn ly th t  nhn li mt li khen tng t mt a tr nm, su tui: ng ny ly kho. Chi tit ny cng li ch thch v phng tr ca tc gi dng nh thong cht hi hc. Ngi ta khoc cho mt a tr con nhng danh v, uy quyn ca chn ph cha, song cu ban tng cho thy mi quan tm ca th t ch l ly kho m thi  v  ch l mt a tr v tt c bin thnh tr h.</span><span style=\" font-family:\'MS Shell Dlg 2\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">- Chi tit Thnh thng ang ng, xung quanh c phi tn chu chc, c my ngi cung nhn ang ng xm xt t n phi by hin thc hng lc ni ph cha m khng cn thm mt li bnh lun no.</span><span style=\" font-family:\'MS Shell Dlg 2\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">=&gt; Vit k m chn thc nh vit s.</span><span style=\" font-family:\'MS Shell Dlg 2\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
