"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">- Th hin gin tip qua vic miu t, ghi chp y , t m con ng vo ph, t lc c lnh truyn cho n khi y lnh v ch thnh ch. S xa hoa trong bc tranh hin thc c miu t t n phi by ra trc mt ngi c.</span><span style=\" font-family:\'MS Shell Dlg 2\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">- Th hin trc tip qua cch quan st, li bnh, nhng suy ngh ca tc gi. Tng l con quan, bit n chn phn hoa,  hi, vy m tc gi ko th tng tng c mc  ca s trng l, xa hoa ni ph cha. ng nhn xt: Cnh giu sang ca vua cha thc khc hn ngi thng. Tc gi cn lm mt bi th miu t s rc r sang trng vi li khi qut cui bi: C tri Nam sang nht l y. Quan Chnh ng mi n cm  im Hu m l dp  tc gi mc s th s n ni ph cha  ton ca ngon vt l, mm vng chn bc lp lnh sng: Ti by gi mi bit cai phong vi cua nha ai gia.</span><span style=\" font-family:\'MS Shell Dlg 2\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
