"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">+ Th , dng dng vi nhng quyn r vt cht, khng ng tnh vi cuc sng no  nhng thiu khi tri va t do</span><span style=\" font-family:\'MS Shell Dlg 2\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt; font-weight:600; font-style:italic;\">b.2) Tm trng ca tc gi khi k n cho th t:</span><span style=\" font-family:\'MS Shell Dlg 2\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">- Hiu ro cn bnh cua th t </span><span style=\" font-family:\'MS Shell Dlg 2\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
