"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">- Kt hp gia vn xui v th ca lm tng tnh cht tr tnh cho tc phm.</span><span style=\" font-family:\'MS Shell Dlg 2\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\"> </span><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">- Kt hp nhiu phng thc biu t nh t s, miu t, biu cm lm gia tng kh nng phn nh hin thc khch quan ca tc phm.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
