"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt; color:#000000;\"> T xa n nay, vic hc lun lun c  cao. Vic hc l mt qu trnh lin tc, lu di, gn b vi con ngi trong sut cuc i.</span><span style=\" font-family:\'MS Shell Dlg 2\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
