"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt; color:#000000;\"> Hnh l g? Hnh l thc hnh. Ly nhng iu  hc p dng  kim nghim thnh k nng.</span><span style=\" font-family:\'MS Shell Dlg 2\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
