"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt; color:#000000;\">+ Trong mi quan h gia hc vi hnh, hc ng vai tr quyt nh. V nu khng hc c nhng kin thc cho mnh, th ly u ra kin thc  vn dng vo thc t cuc sng m kim nghim xem n ng hay sai, tt hay cha tt.</span><span style=\" font-family:\'MS Shell Dlg 2\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt; color:#000000;\">+ Nu ch bit hc l thuyt m khng bit n thc hnh th nhng l thuyt ta hc cng chng c tc dng l bao trong cuc sng. V d: Mt sinh vin hc  ra lm mt bc s phu thut, nu ch hc l thuyt m khng c thc hnh th khi tt nghip ra trng liu tay ngh s ra sao? Hay mt k s nng nghip m ch sut ngy gn vi l thuyt chng thc hnh bao gi, liu l thuyt  hc y c tc dng dng nh th no i vi vic pht trin chn nui, trng trt ca t nc.</span><span style=\" font-family:\'MS Shell Dlg 2\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt; color:#000000;\">--&gt; Chng ta khng c hc l thuyt sung m phi bit p dng nhng l thuyt  vo cuc sng. Chng ta phi bin nhng kin thc  hc thnh nhng tri thc phc v cuc sng.  thc hin c iu , trc ht chng ta phi hc l thuyt tht chc, tht gii.</span><span style=\" font-family:\'MS Shell Dlg 2\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt; font-weight:600; color:#000000;\">M rng, nng cao vn </span><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt; color:#000000;\">:</span><span style=\" font-family:\'MS Shell Dlg 2\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt; color:#000000;\"> Ngy nay, vic hc i i vi hnh  c  cao, c quan tm mt cch nghim tc.</span><span style=\" font-family:\'MS Shell Dlg 2\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt; color:#000000;\"> Nhng vn cn nhng trng hp hc sinh, sinh vin c hc l thuyt nhng t c thc hnh. V d,  mt s trng ph thng, hc l thuyt v mn Ho, mn L, cha th c 100% hc sinh c trc tip lm th nghim,  cc trng hc ngh, cc my mc dng  thc hnh c khi  c k, lc hu so vi thc ti. Nh vy, hnh chng c tc dng.</span><span style=\" font-family:\'MS Shell Dlg 2\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt; color:#000000;\"> Cn ph phn nhng quan im sai lm:</span><span style=\" font-family:\'MS Shell Dlg 2\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt; color:#000000;\">+ Hc m khng thc hnh: Con ngi s tr nn vin vng khng thc t Khi  s nhn vn  mt cch phin din. V d: Trong x hi phong kin Vit Nam, li hc thng dng l &quot;tm chng trch c&quot;. Cui cng nhng k s c o to ch bit sch v, thiu thc tin. T  lm cho x hi b tr tr, km pht trin.</span><span style=\" font-family:\'MS Shell Dlg 2\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
