"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">+ Php o ng nh c tnh khot su thm vo ci s b bng ca tm trng. Tr l ti h, l chai l, khng cn cm gic. Thm vo , hai ch hng nhan (ch dung nhan ngi thiu n) li i vi t &quot;ci&quot; tht l r rng, ma mai. Ci hng nhan tr vi nc non ng l khng ch gi s di du m m hn c l l  s cay ng. Cu th ch ni n hng nhan m li gi ra c s bc phn ca ch th tr tnh. Nhp cu th 1/3/3 cng nh vy, c ch chit, cng khi su vo s b bng khn t.</span><span style=\" font-family:\'MS Shell Dlg 2\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">+ Tuy nhin cu th khng hn ch c ni au, m n cn th hin c bn lnh ca nhn vt tr tnh. Bn lnh y th hin  ngay trong ch tr nh l mt s thch thc vy. T tr kt hp vi nc non th hin s bn gan, s thch . N gi cho ta ngh n mt cu th ca B Huyn Thanh Quan trong bi Thng Long thnh hoi c ( vn tr gan cng tu nguyt).</span><span style=\" font-family:\'MS Shell Dlg 2\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
