"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">+ Cnh tnh Xun Hng th hin qua hnh tng cha ng hai ln bi kch: Trng sp tn (bng x) m vn khuyt cha trn. Cng  l vi Xun Hng, tui xun  tri qua m nhn duyn khng trn vn.</span><span style=\" font-family:\'MS Shell Dlg 2\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
