"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">+ Nhng sinh vt b nh nh m ru kia m vn khng chu phn nh b, hn mn, khng chu yu mm. Tt c nh ang mun bt thot hn ln: ru phi mc &quot;xin ngang mt t&quot;,   rn chc li phi rn chc hn, li phi nhn hot  &quot;m toc chn my&quot;.</span><span style=\" font-family:\'MS Shell Dlg 2\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">+ Ngh thut o ng cng lm ni bt s phn ut ca , ca ru v cng l s phn ut ca tm trng con ngi.</span><span style=\" font-family:\'MS Shell Dlg 2\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">+ Kt hp vi vic s dng nhng ng t mnh (xin, m) vi cc b ng c o (ngang, toc) th hin rt r s bng bnh v ngang ngnh =&gt; , ru nh ang on hn, nh ang phn khng quyt lit vi to ho.</span><span style=\" font-family:\'MS Shell Dlg 2\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
