"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">=&gt; Tuyn ngn khng nh c tnh, s mong mun vt ngoi quan im o c Nho gia thng thng. i vi ng, ngt ngng phi c thc danh v thc ti. Vy ci ngt ngng ca ng khng phi tiu cc m s khng nh bn thn ca mnh, l bn lnh dm sng  i, v mt phong cch sng ti hoa ti t.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt; font-weight:600; font-style:italic;\">e. Gi tr ni dung</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
