"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt; font-weight:600; font-style:italic;\">a. Hnh nh bi ct v con ngi i trn bi ct</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">- Bi ct di li bi ct di: mnh mng dng nh bt tn, nng bng.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">-&gt; Hnh nh t thc, gi con ng i kh khn, nhc nhn, xa xi, m mt.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">-&gt; Hnh nh biu tng: con ng y kh khn m con ngi phi vt qua  i n ch. Mun tm c cn l, tm c ci ch thc c  ngha cho cuc i, con ngi ta phi tri qua v vn kh khn, nhc nhn, th thch.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
