"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">+ Thi gian: mt tri ln vn cn i.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">+ Nc mt ri -&gt; kh nhc, gian trun.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">=&gt; Cnh con ng i xa xi m mt,  cng chnh l con ng i, con ng i n danh li ca k s. Ngi i trn con ng , try trt kh khn, i tt t, vi v khng k thi gian, i vi tm trng au kh, mt mi, chn chng.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
