"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">- Khc ng cng:  ngha biu tng -&gt; ni tuyt vng ca tc gi. ng bt lc v khng th i tip m cng khng bit phi lm g. p  kht vng cao c nhng ng khng tm c con ng  thc hin kht vng . Hay  l nim khao kht thay i cuc sng.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">- Hnh nh thin nhin: pha bc, pha nam u p nhng u kh khn, him tr.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">- Anh ng lm chi trn bi ct?.. cu hi mnh lnh cho bn thn -&gt; phi thot ra khi bi ct danh li y nhc nhn chng gai m v ngha.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">+ Nhp iu th lc nhanh, lc chm, lc dn tr, lc dt khot -&gt; th hin tm trng suy t ca con ng danh li m nh th ang i.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">=&gt; Hnh tng k s c c, l loi y trn tr nhng k v, va qu quyt va tuyt vng trn con ng i tm chn l y chng gai. </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt; font-weight:600; font-style:italic;\">c. Gi tr ni dung</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">- Bi th l s chn ght i vi con ng mu cu danh li tm thng</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">- Tm trng bi phn ca k s cha tm thy li thot trn ng i. Ph phn li hc thut, s bo th tr tr ca triu Nguyn.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
