"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">V d: Trong kho tng vn hc Vit Nam c rt nhiu bi th ni ln thn phn ca ngi ph n phong kin xa. H phi chu s rng buc ca l gio phong kin &quot;</span><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt; font-style:italic;\">Tam tng, t c</span><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">&quot; (</span><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt; font-style:italic;\">ti gia tng ph, xut gi tng phu, phu t tng t v cng dung ngn hnh</span><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">). H hu nh khng c quyn quyt nh cuc i mnh, ch bit sng cam chu v phc tng. Cm thng vi s phn, thn phn v phm cht ca ngi ph n xa, hai nh th H Xun Hng v Trn T Xng  thay h ni ln ting lng mnh qua cc bi th nh:</span><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt; font-style:italic;\">T tnh, Bnh tri nc, Thng v</span><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">...</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt; font-weight:600;\">2. Thn bi</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
