"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">+  bi</span><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt; font-style:italic;\">Thng v</span><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">, hnh nh b T ni bt vi v p ca ngi ph n truyn thng Vit Nam nhn hu, m ang, giu c hi sinh, yu chng thng con ht mc.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt; font-weight:600;\">3. Kt bi:</span><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\"> Tng kt v nh gi vn  ngh lun. Nu cm ngh ca bn thn.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">V d:</span><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt; font-style:italic;\">Ngy nay thn phn ngi ph n  chim mt v tr quan trng trong gia nh. Bi l ci x hi &quot;Trng nam khinh n&quot;  b xa b m thay vo  l mt x hi &quot;cng bng, bnh ng, nam n bnh quyn&quot;. Nhng khng v th m ngi ph n Vit Nam lm mt i v thun phong m tc vn c ca mnh. V vn gi c phm cht, v p truyn thng ca ngi ph n Vit Nam, m ang tho vc.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
