"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">- Trn c s  thc v ti nng v nhn cch bn thn, Nguyn Cng Tr trong</span><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt; font-style:italic;\">Bi ca ngt ngng</span><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\"> ph trng s ngang tng, s ph cch trong li sng ca ng, li sng t ph hp vi khun kh ca o Nho.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">- Nguyn Cng Tr</span><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt; font-style:italic;\">ngt ngng</span><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">khi hnh o (khi lm quan, thc hin cc chc phn, ng lun t ra thng thn, thm ch dm kin ngh, gp  c cho vua). C c phong cch ngo ngh nh vy v ng c ti nng v tn tm vi s nghip. Khng h lun ci  vinh thn ph gia. Trong i thc, Nguyn Cng Ch nhiu ln lp cng trng v l ngi c ti nng nhiu mt mc d vy ng vn phi chp nhn mt cuc i lm quan khng my thun li (ng b thng ging tht thng).</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">- Sau khi t quan, cch ng ngh v chi cng rt ngng, rt khc thng. ng eo mo vo ui b ni l  &quot;</span><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt; font-style:italic;\">che ming th gian</span><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">&quot;, ng dn cc c gi tr ln cha, ng i ht  o v t nh gi cao cc vic lm y. ng c quyn</span><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt; font-style:italic;\">ngt ngng</span><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">v ng v hu trong danh d, sau khi  cng hin rt nhiu cho t nc. Theo ng, iu quan trng nht ca nh nho l hot ng thc tin ch khng phi np sng un mnh theo d lun. ng thch ht ni v  l mn ngh thut ng say m t nh. V th khi v hu ng vn i ht v khng mun t ra mnh l mt bc phi phm, khc i nh cc thnh nhn.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
