"<p align=\"center\" style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:14pt; font-weight:600; font-style:italic;\">----THC HNH V NGHA CA T TRONG S DNG----</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt; font-weight:600;\">Cu 1 (trang 74 SGK Ng vn 11 tp 1)</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt; font-weight:600;\">a. Trong cu th &quot;L vng trc gi kh a vo&quot;, t &quot;l&quot; c dng theo ngha gc hay ngha chuyn? Hy xc nh ngha .</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">Trong cu th &quot;L vng trc gi kh a vo&quot; (Nguyn Khuyn - Thu iu), t &quot;l&quot; c dng theo ngha gc.  l ngha: Ch b phn ca cy, thng  trn ngn hay trn cnh cy, thng c mu xanh, hnh dng mng, c b mt. y l ngha c ngay t khi t &quot;l&quot; xut hin trong ting Vit.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt; font-weight:600;\">b. Trong ting Vit, t &quot;l&quot; cn c dng theo nhiu ngha khc trong nhng trng hp sau: l gan, l phi,... Hy xc nh ngha ca t &quot;l&quot; trong mi trng hp k trn, cho bit c s v phng thc chuyn ngha ca t &quot;l&quot;.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">Trong ting Vit, t &quot;l&quot; cn c dng theo nhiu ngha khc nh:</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">- Trong cc t: L gan, l phi, l m, l lch,... t &quot;l&quot; c dng vi cc t ch cc b phn trong c th ngi.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">- Trong cc t: L th, l n, l thip, l phiu, l bi,... t &quot;l&quot; dng vi cc t ch vt bng giy.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">- Trong cc t: L bum, l c,... t &quot;l&quot; dng  ch cc vt bng vi.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">- Trong cc t: L ct, l chiu, l chn, l thuyn,... t &quot;l&quot; dng vi cc t ch vt bng tre, na, c,...</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
