"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\"> Trong tt c cc trng hp trn, t &quot;l&quot; tuy c dng vi cc trng ngha khc nhau, nhng vn c im chung,  l:</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">- Khi dng vi cc ngha , t l gi tn cc s vt khc nhau, nhng cc vt  c im ging nhau (tng ng): u l cc vt c hnh dng mng, dt, c b mt nh ci l cy.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
