"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt; font-weight:600;\">Cu 2 (trang 74 SGK Ng vn 11 tp 1)Cc t c ngha gc ch b phn c th ngi (u, chn, tay,...) c th chuyn ngha  ch c con ngi. Hy t cu vi mi t  theo ngha ch c con ngi.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
