"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">+ </span><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt; font-style:italic;\">Chu (li):</span><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\"> Thun theo ngi khc theo mt l no  m mnh c th khng hi lng. Dng t &quot;chu&quot;, Kiu t c thi  va tn trng em gi mnh va ni p, ng thi coi trng tnh cm cao qu i vi Kim Trng.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
