"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">- Bu bn, c ngha khi qut, ch c mt tp th nhiu ngi, li c sc thi gn gi ca khu ng. Vi cu  nu ch ng Vit Nam (s t, trang trng) nn khng th dng t bu bn.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
