"<p align=\"center\" style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:14pt; font-weight:600; font-style:italic;\">----N TP VN HC TRUNG I VIT NAM----</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt; font-weight:600;\">I - NI DUNG</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt; font-weight:600;\">1. Nhng biu hin ca ni dung yu nc trong vn hc t th k XVIII n ht th k XIX? So vi giai on trc, ni dung yu nc trong vn hc giai on ny c biu hin g mi.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">- Ni dung yu nc: yu thin nhin, t nc, nim t ho dn tc, lng cm th gic,  ch chin u bt khut chng gic ngoi xm.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">- Bn cnh nhng ni dung yu nc  c trong vn hc cc giai on trc,  giai on vn hc ny (t th k XVIII n ht th k XIX) xut hin nhng ni dung mi:</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">+  thc v vai tr ca ngi tr thc i vi t nc (Chiu cu hin - Ng Th Nhm)</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">+ T tng canh tn t nc (Xin lp khoa lut - Nguyn Trng T)</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">+ Tm hng i mi cho cuc i trong hon cnh x hi b tc (Bi ca ngn i trn bi ct - Cao B Qut),...</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">- Ch ngha yu nc trong vn hc na cui th k XIX cn mang m hng bi trng, th hin c bit r nt trong nhng sng tc ca Nguyn nh Chiu.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt; font-weight:600;\">2. Theo anh (ch) v sao c th ni vn hc t th k XVIII n ht th k XIX xut hin tro lu nhn o ch ngha? Hy ch ra nhng biu hin phong ph, a dng ca ni dung nhn o trong giai on ny. Anh (ch) hy cho bit: vn  c bn nht ca ni dung nhn o trong vn hc th k XVIII n ht th k XIX l g?</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">- Vn hc t th k XVIII n ht th k XIX xut hin mt tro lu nhn o ch ngha. C th ni, ch ngha nhn o trong giai on ny tr thnh mt tro lu bi trong i sng vn hc xut hin lin tip hng lot nhng tc phm mang ni dung nhn o c gi tr ln nh Truyn Kiu, Chinh ph ngm, Cung on ngm, th H Xun Hng,...</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">- Nhng ni dung ch o ch yu th hin trong vn hc giai on ny l:</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">+ S thng cm trc bi kch v ng cm vi kht vng ca con ngi;</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">+ Khng nh,  cao ti nng, nhn phm, ln n nhng th lc tn bo ch p con ngi;</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">+  cao truyn thng o l, nhn ngha ca dn tc.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">- Cm hng nhn o trong giai on ny cng c nhng biu hin mi so vi cc giai on vn hc trc:</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">+ Hng vo quyn sng ca con ngi, nht l con ngi trn th (Truyn Kiu, th H Xun Hng);</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">+  thc v c nhn m nt hn ( thc v quyn sng c nhn, hnh phc c nhn, ti nng c nhn,.... qua cc tc phm nh c Tiu Thanh k - Nguyn Du, T tnh (bi II) - H Xun Hng, Bi ca ngt ngng - Nguyn Cng Tr).</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt; font-weight:600;\">3. Phn tch gi tr phn nh v ph phn hin thc ca on trch Vo ph cha Trnh.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt; font-weight:600; font-style:italic;\">a. M bi:</span><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\"> Gii thiu khi qut v tc gi, tc phm ca on trch (Nu lun im ca )</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt; font-weight:600; font-style:italic;\">b. Thn bi:</span><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\"> Cn trin khai r cc  sau:</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt; font-style:italic;\">* Bc tranh hin thc v cuc sng xa hoa ni ph cha:</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\"> - Quang cnh ni ph cha hin ln cc k xa hoa, trng l v khng km phn tn nghim. Cnh ni ln uy quyn tt bc ca nh cha. Nhng ting qut tho, truyn lnh, nhng ting d ran, nhng con ngi oai v, nhng con ngi khm nm, s st c nhng ca gc, mi vic u c quan truyn mnh, ch dn. Thy thuc khm bnh phi ch, nn th, khm nm, ly t.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\"> - Cng vi s xa hoa l cung cch sinh hot y kiu cch: t ni  n tin nghi, t vt dng n  n thc ung. n c vic i ng, ni nng cng v cng kiu cch.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt; font-style:italic;\">* Cuc sng ni Trnh ph thiu sinh kh v cng.  cng l nguyn nhn gy ra s m yu ca thi t Cn. S thm nghim kiu m cung cng lm tng m kh ni ph cha.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">- Qua cch ni ma mai chm bim ca tc gi, ta thy s lng quyn ca nh cha vi quyn uy ti thng v np sng hng th cc k xa hoa ca cha Trnh cng gia nh; s tht b nhn ca vua L khi y Cuc sng vt cht y  giu sang nhng phm cht tinh thn,  ch ngh lc trng rng.  cng chnh l hnh nh suy yu mc rung ca tp on phong kin L  Trnh nhng nm cui th k XVIII.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">- Qua cch miu t ngi t cnh rt khch quan, tc gi  ngm ph phn kn o cnh giu sang xa hoa quyn uy gh gm ca cha Trnh ng thi th hin tm hn cao thng, kht khao cuc sng t do khng mng danh li ca v danh y Hi Thng Ln ng.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt; font-weight:600; font-style:italic;\">c. Kt bi:</span><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\"> Khng nh li vn  v lin h bn thn.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt; font-weight:600;\">4. Nhng gi tr ni dung v ngh thut ca th vn Nguyn nh Chiu? Ti sao ni, Vn t ngha s Cn Giuc, ln u tin trong vn hc dn tc c mt tng i bi trng v bt t v ngi nng dn ngha s.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">- </span><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt; font-style:italic;\">Gi tr ni dung:</span><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\"> Ni bt nht trong sng tc ca Nguyn nh Chiu l ni dung  cao o l nhn ngha qua Truyn Lc Vn Tin v ni dung yu nc qua Ng Tiu y thut vn p, Chy Ty v nht l qua Vn t ngha s Cn Giuc.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">- </span><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt; font-style:italic;\">Gi tr ngh thut:</span><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\"> ng gp ni bt nht ca Nguyn nh Chiu v ngh thut l tnh cht o c - tr tnh, mu sc Nam B qua ngn ng, hnh tng ngh thut.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">- </span><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt; font-style:italic;\">L gii:</span><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\"> Trc Nguyn nh Chiu, vn hc dn tc cha c mt hnh tng hon chnh v ngi anh hng nng dn ngha s. Trong Vn t ngha s Cn Giuc, hnh tng ngi anh hng nng dn ngha s mang v p bi trng bi  hnh tng ny c s kt hp gia yu t bi (au thng) vi yu t trng (ho hng). Yu t bi c gi ln t i sng lam l, vt v, t ni au thng, mt mt ca ngi ngha s v ting khc xt au ca ngi cn sng. Yu t trng th hin  lng cm th gic, lng yu nc, hnh ng qu cm, anh hng ca ngha qun, s ngi ca cng c nhng ngi  hi sinh v qu hng, t nc. Ting khc trong Vn t ngha s Cn Giuc l ting khc au thng m ln lao, cao c.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; background-color:#ffffff;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt; font-weight:600; color:#000000;\">II. PHNG PHP</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
