"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">- Ni dung hin i ho vn hc din ra trn mi mt,  nhiu phng din: Quan nim v vn hc, t tng, tnh cm, ci nhn,... ca nh vn trc hin thc cuc sng. Tuy nhin hin i ho d nhn thy nht  hnh thc ca vn hc.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt; font-style:italic;\">* Nhn t to iu kin hin i ha vn hc</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">- X hi thc dn na phong kin, c cu x hi c nhng bin i su sc: xut hin cc giai cp, tng lp mi.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">- nh hng ca vn ha phng Ty (Php).</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">- Lc lng sng tc ch yu: Tng lp tr thc Ty hc (tip cn vi nn vn hc Php).</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">- Ch quc ng  thay th ch Hn v ch nm trong nhiu lnh vc.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">- Ngh in, xut bn, bo ch, dch thut ra i v pht trin kh mnh.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">- S xut hin ca i ng ph bnh vn hc.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt; font-style:italic;\">* Qu trnh hin i ho ca vn hc thi k ny din ra qua ba giai on:</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
