"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">- Giai on th ba (khong t nm 1930 n nm 1945).</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\"> Hin i ho vn hc l mt qu trnh.  hai giai on u, c bit  giai on th nht, vn hc cn b nhiu rng buc, nu ko ca ci c, to nn tnh cht giao thi ca vn hc. n giai on th ba, cng cuc hin i ho mi thc s ton din v su sc, hon tt qu trnh hin i ho vn hc.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt; font-weight:600;\">b. Vn hc Vit Nam t u th k XX n cch mng thng Tm c s phn ha phc tp nh th no? Nhng im khc nhau gia hai b phn vn hc cng khai v khng cng khai?</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">- Vn hc Vit Nam t u th k XX n Cch mng thng Tm nm 1945 hnh thnh theo hai b phn v phn ho thnh nhiu dng, va u tranh vi nhau, va b sung cho nhau  cng pht trin.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">- Do c im ca mt nc thuc a, chu s chi phi mnh m v su sc ca qu trnh u tranh gii phng dn tc, vn hc t u th k XX n Cch mng thng Tm nm 1945 hnh thnh hai b phn: Vn hc cng khai v vn hc khng cng khai.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">- Vn hc cng khai l vn hc hp php, tn ti trong vng php lut ca chnh quyn thc dn phong kin. Vn hc khng cng khai b t ra ngoi vng php lut, phi lu hnh b mt. Do khc nhau v c im ngh thut, v khuynh hng thm m, nn vn hc cng khai li phn ho thnh nhiu dng, trong  ni ln hai dng chnh: Vn hc lng mn v vn hc hin thc.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">- B phn vn hc khng cng khai c th vn cch mng b mt, c bit l th ca cc ch s v cc chin s cch mng sng tc trong t.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt; font-weight:600;\">c. Vn hc Vit Nam t u th k XX n cch mng thng Tm pht trin vi nhp  ht sc nhanh chng. Hy gii thch nguyn nhn ca nhp  pht trin y?</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">- Vn hc Vit Nam t u th k XX n Cch mng thng Tm 1945 pht trin vi nhp  ht sc nhanh chng. S pht trin ny th hin rt r  s pht trin ca th trong phong tro Th mi,  cc th loi nh truyn ngn, tiu thuyt, phng s, l lun v ph bnh vn hc,...</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">- Nhng nguyn nhn lm cho vn hc thi k ny pht trin nhanh chng l:</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">+ Do s thc bch ca yu cu thi i;</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">+ Do yu cu ch quan ca nn vn hc (y l nguyn nhn chnh);</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">+ S thc tnh, tri dy mnh m ca ci ti c nhn.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">+ Ngoi ra, cng cn phi nhn thy rng, thi k ny, vn chng  tr thnh mt th hng ho, vit vn tr thnh mt ngh  kim sng. y l l do thit thc, mt nhn t kch thch ngi cm bt.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt; font-weight:600;\">Cu 2 (trang 91 SGK Ng vn 11 tp 1)</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt; font-weight:600;\">a. Nhng truyn thng t tng ln nht, su sc nht ca vn hc Vit Nam l g? Vn hc Vit Nam t u th k XX n cch mng thng Tm c ng gp g cho truyn thng y?</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">- Vn hc Vit Nam c hai truyn thng ln: Ch ngha yu nc v ch ngha nhn o. Thi k vn hc t u th k XX n Cch mng thng Tm nm 1945  k tha v pht trin nhng truyn thng , ng thi em n cho truyn thng y mt ng gp mi ca thi i: Tinh thn dn ch.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">- Tinh thn dn ch em n cho truyn thng nhn o nhng nt mi:</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">+ Quan tm ti nhng con ngi bnh thng trong x hi, nht l tng lp nhn dn cc kh, lm than.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">+T co p bc bc lt m cn th hin su sc kht vng mnh lit ca mi c nhn,  cao v p hnh thc, phm gi v pht huy cao  ti nng ca mi con ngi.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt; font-weight:600;\">b. Nhng th loi vn hc no mi xut hin trong vn hc Vit Nam t u th k XX n cch mng thng Tm? S cch tn, hin i ha cc th loi tiu thuyt v th din ra nh th no?</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">- Trong giai on vn hc ny, xut hin nhiu nhng th loi mi nh phng s, l lun ph bnh vn hc v nhng th loi c c s bin chuyn v cht nh tiu thuyt, th. C th ni, s cch tn hin i ho v th loi th hin r nht  tiu thuyt v th.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">- Tiu thuyt trung i Vit Nam thng vay mn  ti, ct truyn ca vn hc Trung Quc; tp trung vo vic xy dng ct truyn ly k, hp dn; kt cu theo kiu chng hi v theo cng thc; kt thc c hu; truyn c thut theo trnh t thi gian; nhn vt thng phn tuyn rch ri; cu vn theo li bin ngu,... Trong khi , tiu thuyt hin i xo b nhng c im trn. Tiu thuyt hin i ly tnh cch nhn vt lm trung tm, ch trng tnh cch hn l ct truyn, i su vo th gii ni tm nhn vt. Tiu thuyt trn thut theo thi gian t nhin m rt linh hot; kt thc thng khng c hu; b nhng c l, dng bt php t thc; li vn t nhin gn vi li n ting ni hng ngy,..</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">- Th mi khc th trung i  ch n ph b cc quy phm cht ch v h thng c l ca th trung i (v nim, lut, in c, hnh nh c l,...). Th mi l ting ni ca ci ti c nhn trc to vt, trc cuc i. Thot ra khi nhng quy phm cht ch v h thng c l dy c ca th trung i, ci ti Th mi c gii phng v tnh cm, cm xc, ng thi n trc tip nhn th gii bng cp mt &quot;xanh non&quot; khin n pht hin ra nhiu iu mi l v thin nhin v lng ngi.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt; font-weight:600;\">Luyn tp</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt; font-weight:600;\">Cu hi (trang 91 SGK Ng vn 11 tp 1)V sao c th gi vn hc Vit Nam t nm 1900 n nm 1930 c gi l giai on vn hc giao thi?</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">- Vn hc ca c giai on 1900 - 1930 c tnh cht giao thi:</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">+ Tnh cht giao thi  c biu hin  s tn ti song song hai nn vn hc c v mi vi hai lc lng sng tc, hai cng chng vi hai quan nim vn hc, hai ngn ng vn hc  hai a bn khc nhau,  xu th thng li ca nn vn hc mi ang tin ti thay th nn vn hc c ang suy yu dn. </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">+ S i mi gp phi nhiu ro cn</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; font-size:13pt;\">+ S nu ko ca nhng ci c</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
