"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:115%;\"><span style=\" font-size:13pt; font-weight:600;\">1. Ni dung quy lut gi tr</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:115%;\"><span style=\" font-size:13pt;\">-</span><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; font-size:7pt;\"> </span><span style=\" font-size:13pt; font-style:italic;\">SX v lu thng HH phi da trn thi gian lao ng x hi cn thit  SX ra HH</span><span style=\" font-size:13pt;\"> .</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:115%;\"><span style=\" font-size:13pt;\">Ni dung ql gi tr c biu hin trong SX v lu thng HH:</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:115%;\"><span style=\" font-size:13pt; font-weight:600; font-style:italic;\">+ Trong sn xut:</span><span style=\" font-size:13pt;\"> QL gi tr yu cu ngi SX phi m bo sao cho thi gian lao ng c bit (TGLCB)  SX HH ph hp vi thi gian lao ng x hi cn thit (TGLXHCT)</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:115%;\"><span style=\" font-size:13pt; font-weight:600;\">* </span><span style=\" font-size:13pt; font-weight:600; text-decoration: underline;\">Nhn xt s  1</span><span style=\" font-size:13pt; font-weight:600;\">:</span><span style=\" font-size:13pt;\"> phn a</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:115%;\"><span style=\" font-size:13pt;\">-</span><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; font-size:7pt;\"> </span><span style=\" font-size:13pt;\">Ngi (1) TGLCB = TGLXHCT, thc hin ng y/c ql gi tr, nn thu c li nhun trung bnh.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:115%;\"><span style=\" font-size:13pt;\">-</span><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; font-size:7pt;\"> </span><span style=\" font-size:13pt;\">Ngi (2) TGLCB &lt; TGLXHCT, thc hin tt ql gi tr, nn thu c li nhun nhiu hn mc li nhun trung bnh.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:115%;\"><span style=\" font-size:13pt;\">-</span><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; font-size:7pt;\"> </span><span style=\" font-size:13pt;\">Ngi (3) TGLCB &gt; TGLXHCT, vi phm y/c ql gi tr, nn b thua l.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:115%;\"><span style=\" font-size:13pt;\">+</span><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; font-size:7pt;\"> </span><span style=\" font-size:13pt; font-weight:600; font-style:italic;\">Trong lu thng:</span><span style=\" font-size:13pt;\"> QL gi tr yu cu vic trao i gia hai HH A v B phi da trn TGLXHCT (phi </span><span style=\" font-size:13pt; font-style:italic;\">theo nguyn tc ngang gi).</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:115%;\"><span style=\" font-size:13pt; font-weight:600;\">a) </span><span style=\" font-size:13pt; font-weight:600; text-decoration: underline;\">i vi 1 hng ho: (S  2)</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:115%;\"><span style=\" font-size:13pt;\">Gi c hh c th bn cao, thp so vi gi tr ca n, nhng xoay xung quanh trc gi tr hh.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:115%;\"><span style=\" font-size:13pt; font-weight:600;\">b) </span><span style=\" font-size:13pt; font-weight:600; text-decoration: underline;\">i vi tng hh v trn ton xh</span><span style=\" font-size:13pt; font-weight:600;\">:</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:115%;\"><span style=\" font-size:13pt; font-weight:600;\">*</span><span style=\" font-size:13pt; font-weight:600; text-decoration: underline;\">Ql gi tr y/c</span><span style=\" font-size:13pt; font-weight:600;\">:</span><span style=\" font-size:13pt;\"> Tng gi c hh sau khi bn = tng gi tr hh trong SX.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
