"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:115%;\"><span style=\" font-size:13pt; font-weight:600;\">2.</span><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; font-size:7pt;\"> </span><span style=\" font-size:13pt; font-weight:600;\">a) Ngun gc ca nh nc</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:115%;\"><span style=\" font-size:13pt; font-style:italic;\">- XH cng sn nguyn thy cha c nh nc v:</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:115%;\"><span style=\" font-size:13pt;\">+ Trnh  ca LLSX cn thp km, khi lng sn phm ch  nhu cu ti thiu ca cc thnh vin trong XH.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:115%;\"><span style=\" font-size:13pt;\">+ Khng c d tha lm ca ring, cha c t hu v ti sn, cha c s phn chia giai cp, cha c s bc lt, do  cha c nh nc.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:115%;\"><span style=\" font-size:13pt; font-style:italic;\">- Nh nc u tin trong lch s xut hin:</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:115%;\"><span style=\" font-size:13pt;\">+ Thi k cui ca XH CSNT LLSX pht trin, s phn cng lao ng XH c m rng lm cho NSL tng ln, sn phm ngy cng nhiu, xut hin iu kin chim ot ca ci d tha lm ti sn ring, ngi c a v (t trng, th lnh qun s) chim ot ti sn.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:115%;\"><span style=\" font-size:13pt;\">+ Nh vy, qu trnh t hu ti sn din ra, ch  t hu hnh thnh, XH phn chia thnh g/c i lp nhau: g/c bc lt v g/c b bc lt.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:115%;\"><span style=\" font-size:13pt;\">+ Do li ch i lp nn mu thun g/c ngy cng gay gt khng th iu ho;  duy tr qun l XH, i hi mt t chc quyn lc mi, t chc  do g/c chim u th v kinh t thit lp s thng tr g/c bo v li ch v a v ca mnh. T chc  l nh nc.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
